pageProduct.description:
General Information

SAY GOODNIGHT TO RESTLESS NIGHTS
Has the relentless isolation made for some restless nights? Stop trying to sleep it off and try our Wellness Bundle instead, it’s full of products to help support a restful night’s sleep.

THE TALE OF THE YAWNICORN
After unexpected hibernation sent its body clock into shock, lack of sleep has turned both daytime and bedtime into a waking nightmare for the poor Yawnicorn.
Now it spends its days flexing its jaw muscles as it emits its distinctive low, yawning call and watching the bags under its eyes turn into suitcases.
This pack has been designed to help the sleep deprived Yawnicorn say goodnight to bad nights’ sleep once and for all.

Common Uses

Grab a great deal and stop counting sheep with the Swisse Yawnicorn Wellness Bundle. Hurry, the savings await!

Ingredients

Swisse Ultiboost Magnesium + Sleep Powder is a premium quality formula containing a unique blend of eight nutrients and herbs including choline, inositol, hops and passionflower.

Swisse Argan Revitalising Eye Cream is an ultra-hydrating formula that replenishes and refines the delicate under-eye area to prevent signs of premature aging for a more youthful and rested appearance.

Swisse Manuka Honey Detoxifying Clay Mask is a luxurious facial treatment formulated to draw out impurities and toxins, refine pores and improve skin texture to reveal a glowing, smooth complexion
